# EAS upload ignore.
# The parent repo (/Users/rattee/Developer/PhysioAI) gitignores all of `App/`
# ("local-only app code"), so EAS — which otherwise selects files via git — would
# upload nothing. With this .easignore present, EAS archives App/Patient directly,
# honoring only these excludes. Keep src/, assets/ (incl. the ~15 MB .task pose
# models), plugins/, and the config files so the cloud build has everything.
node_modules/
.expo/
ios/
android/
*.log
.DS_Store
